column5: I found a tackle box full of tackle on Saturday while fishing on the Grand.  I took a quick look around for the owner after being in the same spot for close to four hours.  I know the chances are slim but if it is yours shoot me a p.m and we will get it back where it belongs.
Yet another outstanding member!!. Hope it gets back to whom it belongs.
Kudos to ya I hope the owner is on the board.
if you tell me whats in it, I'll tell u if it's mine - jokes- but good to hear there are lots of good people out there still.
Actually if its beige plaino and you found it at the Wilkes dam in Brantford I know whos it is..My buddies Kid lost his while fishing down there..Man is he ticked....
Wow! Hope it's his! Great work HA.
Sorry T.B it is not that same one, I was under the bridge in Caladonia.
